{"tid":2058561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"親俄左膠串「連登仔」, 炮轟「黎智英」抹黑美國黑人示威, 「黃之鋒」靠攏極右","createTime":"2020-06-10T09:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T13:19:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ada839d0395c798d659b1ae28bb87dc88db059aa","tid":2058561,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"親俄左膠=表面係左膠, 實際上係親俄.<br />\n<br />\n好似親俄左膠網站The Grayzone的負責人Max Blumenthal, 就經常上俄羅斯官媒發言. (另一方面, 親俄左膠有一掛都企圖痴Trump陣營, Max Blumenthal都上過Fox News訪問)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>而家, The Grayzone公開指責「黎智英」和「黃之鋒」, 兼串埋連登仔:</strong><br />\n- 黎智英分享Avi Yemini條片講美國黑人示威同香港示威有咩唔同 . 黎智英咁做, 擺明係抹黑美國黑人示威.<br />\n- 黎智英接受cnn訪問, 指出只有Trump才可救香港.<br />\n<br />\n- 香港人示威, 都高舉&lt;President Trump, please liberate Hong Kong!&gt;<br />\n<br />\n-  借用香港(極左膠)人士wilfred chan之言: 香港連登仔以為反Trump既人就一定係親中共.<br />\n<br />\n- 黃之鋒口講支持美國黑人示威, 但實際上, 黃之鋒與大量美國共和黨議員關係密切. 果d共和黨議員全部係極右.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thegrayzone.com/2020/06/09/hong-kongs-far-right-us-politicians-crush-black-lives-matter/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthegrayzone.com%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2Fhong-kongs-far-right-us-politicians-crush-black-lives-matter%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=4601c56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thegrayzone.com/2020/06/09/hong-kongs-far-right-us-politicians-crush-black-lives-matter/</a>"},{"pid":"d578bac57bffd6c8e388717d4a9fd5f72e7cfa69","tid":2058561,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯出手抹黑香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nwilfred chan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d66270a986eb8d559a2bb6bd4542853f84a313","tid":2058561,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74282e0227a88